    "body": "I created simple script using flask, it run smoothly, but when using `app.run(debug=True)` it returns 404 error\r\nRun with:\r\n`export FLASK_APP=main.py`\r\n\r\n`flask run`\r\n\r\n\r\n```python\r\nfrom flask import Flask,request\r\napp = Flask(__name__)\r\napp.run(debug=True)\r\n@app.route('/')\r\ndef hello_world():\r\n    return 'hellow'\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt return 404 error\r\n\r\n```pytb\r\n127.0.0.1 - - [15/Jul/2017 16:41:56] \"GET / HTTP/1.1\" 404 -\r\n127.0.0.1 - - [15/Jul/2017 16:43:03] \"GET /favicon.ico HTTP/1.1\" 404 -\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Environment\r\n\r\n* Python version: 3.5.3\r\n* Flask version: 0.12.2\r\n* Werkzeug version: 0.12.1\r\n",
